Package: whozr
Type: Package
Title: Convert Raw Anthrops to WHO Z-Scores
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Simon Schoenbuchner
Description: Convert between raw anthropometric measurement (weight, height,
    length, etc) and z-scores, using the WHO growth references for 0-5 and 5-19
    year-olds. Contains functions for calculating z-scores (or reversing to
    anthrops), rounding numbers, and formatting output for tables.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: dplyr (>= 0.7.5), tibble (>= 1.4.2)
